\cf0 1. Product Overview\
\pard\pardeftab720\li200\sa200\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f1\b \cf0 One-liner: 
\f2\b0 Artivaa is an AI-powered meeting intelligence platform that joins your calls, records and transcribes them, turns conversations into structured summaries and action items, and helps teams collaborate through workspaces and integrations.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa120\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f1\b \cf0 Live product: 
\f2\b0 https://artivaa-frontend.vercel.app\

\f1\b Mission: 
\f2\b0 Make every meeting actionable \'97 automatically.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa200\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f1\b \cf0 Vision: 
\f2\b0 Become the default meeting intelligence layer for modern teams \'97 join, record, understand, share, execute \'97 across any video platform.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa80\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

